'''Brant''' is a research assistant who worked under [[Miriam Alba]].

==History==
Brant worked under [[Miriam Alba]], researching a cure for lymphoma. When a series of explosions at the hospital forced an evacuation, Brant helped move research out of the building.

==Career==
He was a research assistant at [[Pacific Northwest General Hospital]], working under [[Miriam Alba]] until her death.
